Find Average of Array
Problem:
Find the average of an array of integers.

Input: An integer array.
Output: The average value.


CODE:



public class demo {
    
    //CREATE METHOD
    
    public static double avarageValue(int [] arr1 ){
        
        int sum = 0;
        
        for(int i = 0; i < arr1.length; i++){
            
            sum = sum + arr1[i];
            
        }
        
        return (double) sum / arr1.length;
    }
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    public static void main(String [] args){
        int [] arr = {7, 9, 5, 25, 10};
        
        double results = avarageValue(arr);
        
        System.out.println(results);
    }
}
    




ANOTHER PROCESS CODE :

public class Main {
    public static double findAverage(int[] arr) {
        int sum = 0;
        for (int num : arr) {
            sum += num;
        }
        return (double) sum / arr.length;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] arr = {5, 3, 8, 1, 4};
        System.out.println("Average value: " + findAverage(arr));
    }
}
